title: Missing man found deceased after police search
content: A 63-YEAR-OLD Rockhampton man reported missing south of Gladstone last Friday was found deceased yesterday, according to Queensland Police.    The discovery followed a public appeal for information and an extensive search of bushland between Agnes Water and Turkey Beach last week involving police on trail bikes and a rescue helicopter.    There were no suspicious circumstances.    Police will prepare a report for the Coroner in relation to the death.    Related Items
